you must first install Terraform in order to deploy this ansible playbook 

https://www.terraform.io/intro/getting-started/install.html

Please add your access_key and secret_key to build.tf 

Please add your Key Pair to the key_name in build.tf

Just run terraform plan to see your results and then run terraform apply to build your ec2 instance

TO DEPLOY YOUR WEBAPP RUN THE ANSIBLE PLAYBOOK BELOW!!!

<ansible-playbook -i host deploy_mydemosite.yml>

TO UPDATE YOUR INSTANCE RUN THE PLAYBOOK BELOW

Please edit your ansible host file and add your hostname or IP address of your EC2 instance and run <ansible-playbook -i host update-webapp.yml>
